snippet.title: Sea Stars - Trailer (Google Play)
snippet.description:
Available for FREE in the Google Play Store!
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hotheadgames.android.seastars

One touch controls are all you need to guide the incredible Sea Stars through a sea full of coins and underwater dangers. Dive deep to pick up speed and leap from the water to somersault and avoid the angry jellies and rocket crabs along your path. 

HIGHLIGHTS 
★ Swim as far as you can to explore this colorful world and complete the fun missions 
★ Explore an underwater world full of desert islands, sunken cities and treasure-laden shipwrecks. 
★ Find exciting free prizes inside clam shells or spend your hard earned coins in the store to buy power-ups or more Sea Stars characters. 

MORE COOL CHARACTERS 
★ Dante the Dolphin 
★ Oscar the Orca 
★ Teeter the Otter 
★ Shelly the Sea Turtle 
★ Mr Puddles the Penguin 
★ Niji the Narwhal, (the very rare and colorful "unicorn of the sea") and many more
